    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Changing lives since 2009</span>
    <h1>Every act of kindness builds a brighter future.</h1>
    <p>We partner with communities to deliver clean water, education, and hope where it's needed most. Your support today becomes someone's new beginning tomorrow.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Projects →</a>
      <a href="#volunteer" class="btn btn-ghost">🤝 Become a Volunteer</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section class="stats">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stats-card">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="num">10k+</div><div class="label">Lives Impacted</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78L12 21.23l8.84-8.84a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="num">50+</div><div class="label">Active Projects</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="num">20+</div><div class="label">Global Partners</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROJECTS -->
<section class="projects" id="projects">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="projects-head">
      <h2 class="serif">Projects changing lives right now</h2>
      <p>Choose a cause close to your heart. Every contribution moves us closer to a world where no one is left behind.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="project-grid">

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541252260730-0412e8e2108e?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop')">
          <span class="tag">Water</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <h3 class="serif">Clean Water Initiative</h3>
          <p>Building wells and water systems to bring safe drinking water to remote villages.</p>
          <div class="fund-row"><span>$68,000</span><span class="of">of $100,000</span></div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:68%"></div></div>
          <div class="pct">68% funded</div>
          <a href="#" class="support-btn">Support →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1593113646773-028c64a8f1b8?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop')">
          <span class="tag">Food</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <h3 class="serif">Nourish Communities</h3>
          <p>Delivering nutritious meals and sustainable farming to fight hunger at its root.</p>
          <div class="fund-row"><span>$55,000</span><span class="of">of $60,000</span></div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:92%"></div></div>
          <div class="pct">92% funded</div>
          <a href="#" class="support-btn">Support →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497486751825-1233686d5d80?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop')">
          <span class="tag">Education</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <h3 class="serif">Educate a Child</h3>
          <p>Providing books, supplies, and teachers so every child can learn and thrive.</p>
          <div class="fund-row"><span>$42,000</span><span class="of">of $75,000</span></div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:56%"></div></div>
          <div class="pct">56% funded</div>
          <a href="#" class="support-btn">Support →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIAL -->
<section class="testimonial">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="quote-wrap">
      <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
      <blockquote id="quoteText">Before the well was built, I walked three hours each day for water. Now my children go to school instead. Hopewell gave us back our time and our hope.</blockquote>
      <div class="quote-name" id="quoteName">Amara Okafor</div>
      <div class="quote-role" id="quoteRole">Mother of three, Clean Water Initiative</div>
      <div class="dots">
        <button class="arrow" onclick="shiftQuote(-1)">‹</button>
        <button class="active" data-i="0" onclick="setQuote(0)"></button>
        <button data-i="1" onclick="setQuote(1)"></button>
        <button data-i="2" onclick="setQuote(2)"></button>
        <button class="arrow" onclick="shiftQuote(1)">›</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DONATE -->
<section class="donate" id="donate">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="donate-card">
      <div class="heart"><svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 21s-7.5-4.8-10-9.3C.4 8.4 2 4.5 5.7 4c2-.3 3.9.6 5 2.2C11.9 4.6 13.8 3.7 15.7 4c3.7.5 5.3 4.4 3.7 7.7C19.5 16.2 12 21 12 21z"/></svg></div>
      <h2 class="serif">Your generosity creates real change</h2>
      <p>Choose an amount and give today. Every dollar goes directly toward programs that transform lives.</p>
      <div class="amounts">
        <button class="amount" onclick="selectAmount(this)">$25</button>
        <button class="amount selected" onclick="selectAmount(this)">$50</button>
        <button class="amount" onclick="selectAmount(this)">$100</button>
        <button class="amount" onclick="selectAmount(this)">$250</button>
      </div>
      <div class="donate-actions">
        <a href="#" class="donate-now">Donate Now</a>
        <a href="#" class="donate-link">Set up monthly giving</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

